{
  "stem": "5891.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I had to march with them out in the big main office out in front.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, you know, with soldiers like [INAUDIBLE] soldiers, when they should lay in the hand grenades, and boxes, and all that stuff, office tables, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I said, you want to [? tell us, ?] change your mind?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Isn't that it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he's the guy who had given me that job when I first came, picked me for that job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't too worried about nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured, what the heck, they could only kill me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But if they don't kill me, I got to go out to that munition factory.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's why I was worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I figured, that's the end now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My job's gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, no officer, herr commandant, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would like that to say it any different, but the old man did not.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That man, that officer, did not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had nothing to do with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He don't know nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, he said, well, we will see.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he said, he gave some kind of order to the, the officer there and some military talk, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And before you know it, that [INAUDIBLE] told me to step on that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There's a double hand grenade box there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was, like, milk boxes, the old-fashioned wooden boxes, and they had their hand grenades, and there was two of them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I had to step on that and put my hands in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was somehow they would hook, they hooked me on that with the cord, and I'm staying on the box.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said, what the heck are they going to do to me now?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
